#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:183
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"守卫皱了皱眉头。“不知道你们这些人是怎么到这儿的，但这里不是旅游景点。你们最好"
"别绕路，直接往出口走，这样就不会有麻烦。”接着你听到守卫嘟囔着什么“需要再次加"
"强安保”的话，然后通讯就断了，你意识到他们已经忙着处理下一批到访者了。\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t你继续前行，满心困惑，还有一丝担忧。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:187
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "检查仓库。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:191
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:200
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "这儿就是海盗的老巢，对吧？我们来做点买卖。*Spit*"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:202
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“哦。”守卫似乎有点恼火，要么是厌倦了每次都费劲解释，要么是对你过火的态度不以"
"为然。“你稍微有点搞错了，海盗勾当不是我们的重点，追求不受束缚的进步才更像那么"
"回事。但没错，你可以在这里进行别人口中的非法交易。这对获取我们需要的那种东西"
"非常有用。\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t我会把你的请求告知所有相关方，而你……务必要带够废料。我们喜欢避免"
"不必要的麻烦。”\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t他们把坐标发给你，然后放你过去了。尽管这个星区行事隐秘，但你心里"
"已经清楚，这将会对你的整体声誉产生负面影响。不过，如果你能自己从海盗那里搞到"
"所需的一切，那倒也无关紧要。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:214
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "海盗行径挺带劲的。值了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:222
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "无视他们，试图飞越过去。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:224
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们的武器立刻进入战备状态，显然早料到会有这种情况。也许说几句话就能避免冲突，但他们已经呼叫了增援。\n"
"\t\t\t令人惊讶的是，他们的飞船氧气系统似乎起火了……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:234
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "哈！真是个白痴——"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:236
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"突然间，你听到飞船里传来奇怪的传送声，但没有探测到登舰者，只有热源信号……你的飞船也起火了！而且火势比他们的还要猛烈不少。\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t如果你能挺过这一劫，或许就能弄明白到底发生了什么，以及如何利用这种情况。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:245
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
